<div id="apply-page">
  <div class="plank secondary-md light main-feature under-logo">
    <div class="section-container">
      <section>
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <%= large_modal('intro-video',
                 title: '',
                 content: '<div style="text-align: center">
                            <iframe src="//player.vimeo.com/video/99269824" width="800" height="450" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe> 
                          </div>'
            ) %>
            <blockquote>
              <p>&ldquo;I joined <b>Beyond Z</b> because I wanted to be a part of a <b>community</b> that would help me develop my <b>career skills</b> &hellip;One particular thing that I&rsquo;ve learned is to <b>work together</b> with other people and have <b>confidence</b> in myself&rdquo;</p>
              <footer>
                Cesar Ramirez, UC Berkeley, class of 2017
              </footer>
            </blockquote>
            <i data-toggle="modal" data-target="#intro-video" class="intro-play-button"></i>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="sign-up" class="plank tertiary-md">
    <div class="section-container">
      <section>
        <div class="col-sm-12 text-center">
          <section>
            <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
              <p class="shoutout">You want to develop your skills and expand your network so you can access the best career opportunities.<br />Beyond Z is here to help.</p>
            </div>
          </section>
          <section>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-3">
              <p class="feature">Beyond Z DISCOVERS and DEVELOPS extraordinary, diverse, and driven young people - like you - and CONNECTS them to professional opportunities and networks.</p>
            </div>
          </section>
          <section>
            <div class="col-sm-12">
              <%= apply_button('undergrad_student') %>
              <br /><br />
              <%= light_page_jump 'What to expect', 'what-to-expect' %> |
              <%= light_page_jump 'Who can apply', 'who-can-apply' %> |
              <%= light_page_jump 'Application and Program Timeline', 'application-and-program-timeline' %>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a id="what-to-expect"></a>
  <div class="plank plain-lt">
    <div class="section-container">
      <section>
        <div class="col-lg-6 no-pad what-to-expect-image">
         <%= image_tag 'what_to_expect.jpg' %>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h2>What to expect</h2>
            <p>Through our hybrid online and in-person experience, you'll get:</p>
            <ul>
              <li><b>Skills:</b> learn the hard and soft skills companies and organizations want and practice them in mock professional settings.</li>
              <li><b>Experience:</b> apply skills to solve real-world challenges with a cohort of your peers.</li>
              <li><b>Coaching:</b> receive small group and 1:1 coaching from a local professional to achieve personal and professional goals.</li>
              <li><b>Networking:</b> expand your 'circle of champions' to include motivated peers, supportive adults, and respected thought-leaders.</li>
            </ul>
            <%= sign_up_link('undergrad_student') %>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a id="who-can-apply"></a>
  <div class="plank plain-md">
    <div class="section-container who-can-apply-image-section-container">
      <section>
        <div class="col-md-8 col-md-push-4 no-pad who-can-apply-image-col">
          <%= image_tag 'who_can_apply.jpg' %>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-md-pull-8">
          <h2>Who can apply</h2>
          <p>We’re looking for students who want to develop their career and leadership skills, explore their identity, build meaningful relationships with peers and young adults, accelerate their career, and make the world a better place.</p>
          <h3>Coaches and Speakers</h3>
          <%= learn_more_link 'volunteering', volunteer_path %>
          <!--
          <h3>BZ Overdrive Program (K-12 Students)</h3>
          <%= learn_more_link 'bringing Beyond Z Overdrive to your school', partner_path %>
          -->

          <h3><b>San Jose, CA</b> BZ Accelerator: Life is a Start-Up (College Students)</h3>
          <p>You're eligible to apply if you're:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>An undergraduate student with sophomore or junior standing <i>(between ~30-60 units)</i></li>
            <li>In good academic standing and able to register for Science 90 (3 credits) during the Fall Semester</li>
            <li>Able to commit an average of 6-8 hours a week to this course during the Fall Semester</li>
            <li>Able to attend 3 events outside of scheduled course time (Fri, Aug 21; Sat, Sept 12; Fri, Dec 4)</li>
          </ul>

          <%= sign_up_link('undergrad_student') %>


          <h3><b>New York City</b> BZ Accelerator Program (College Students)</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Must be an undergraduate </li>
            <li>Must have a 2.5 cumulative GPA or higher </li>
            <li>Must be able to commit an average of 2-3 hours a week to Beyond Z from the week of April 20th through the week of May 11th (except on holidays and breaks) </li>
            <li>Must be able to commit to Kick Off (Saturday, April 18) and Closing (Saturday, May 16)</li>
            <li>Spots for our program are limited and we may not be able to accept all qualified applicants at this time.</li>
          </ul>

          <%= sign_up_link('undergrad_student') %>

          <h3><b>Washington, DC</b> BZ Accelerator Program (College Students)</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Must be a freshman at your college or university </li>
            <li>Must have a 2.5 cumulative GPA or higher </li>
            <li>Must be able to commit an average of 2 hours a week to Beyond Z from the week of March 23rd through the week of April 18th (except on holidays and breaks) </li>
            <li>Must be able to commit to Kick Off (Saturday, March 28) and Closing (Saturday, April 18)</li>
            <li>Spots for our program are limited and we may not be able to accept all qualified applicants at this time.</li>
          </ul>

          <%= sign_up_link('undergrad_student') %>

        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a id="application-and-program-timeline"></a>
  <div class="plank plain-lt">
    <div class="section-container">
      <section>
        <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
          <h2>BZ Accelerator college program timeline</h2>

          <h3>San Jose, CA</h3>
          <p>We process applications in the order they are submitted, so applying earlier will give you the greater choice of sections.</p>
          <dl class="timeline">
            <dt>Early Application Deadline</dt>
              <dd>Friday, May 22</dd>
            <dt>Late Application Deadline</dt>
              <dd>Friday, July 31</dd>
            <dt>Welcome Mixer</dt>
              <dd>Friday, August 21</dd>
            <dt>Story of Self</dt>
              <dd>Saturday, September 12</dd>
            <dt>Capstone Presentations and Celebration</dt>
              <dd>Friday, December 4</dd>
          </dl>
          <div class="text-center">
            <%= sign_up_link('undergrad_student') %>
          </div>


          <h3>New York City</h3>
          <dl class="timeline">
            <dt>Application Deadline Extended</dt>
              <dd>Wednesday, March 25</dd>

            <dt>Kick-Off Saturday</dt>
              <dd>April 18</dd>
            <dt>Main Program, 2 hours weekly</dt>
              <dd>Weeks of April 20 - May 11</dd>
            <dt>Closing</dt>
              <dd>Saturday, May 16</dd>
          </dl>
          <div class="text-center">
            <%= sign_up_link('undergrad_student') %>
          </div>


          <h3>Washington, DC</h3>
          <dl class="timeline">
            <dt>Application Deadline</dt>
              <dd>Sunday, March 8</dd>

            <dt>Kick-Off Saturday</dt>
              <dd>March 28</dd>
            <dt>Main Program, 2 hours weekly</dt>
              <dd>Weeks of March 30 - April 13</dd>
            <dt>Closing</dt>
              <dd>Saturday, April 18</dd>
          </dl>
          <div class="text-center">
            <%= sign_up_link('undergrad_student') %>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="plank plain-md">
    <div class="section-container">
      <section>
        <div class="col-sm-4 no-pad">
          <%= image_tag 'aimee.jpg', width: '100%' %>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-8">
          <blockquote>
            “This next generation of extraordinary, diverse future leaders is compelled to pay it forward for those who come after them...and to recognize all those who came before them, on whose shoulders they stand.”
            <footer>Aimee Eubanks Davis, Founder</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
